{"_id":"AogvWt2EKrylzBPQ","name":"Mage Talents - Magus","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a black mage gains experience, he learns a number of talents that assist him in manipulating spells and other forms of magic. At 2nd level and every two levels thereafter, a black mage gains one mage talent. A black mage cannot select an individual talent more than once. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a black mage&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>A magus only has access to the following mage talents: Concentrate, Empowered Magic, Mage Training, Silent Spell, Spell Guard, Spell Lore, Spell Sage, Still Spell.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of mage talents can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/black-mage/mage-talents/\">Mage Talents</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"advanced-mage-talents\">Advanced Mage Talents</h3>\n<p>At 12th, and every two levels thereafter, a black mage learns further talents to assist him in manipulating spells and other forms of magic. He may choose one of the following advanced mage talents in place of a mage talent. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a black mage&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>A magus only has access to the following advanced mage talents: Augment Spell, Maximized Magic, Quickened Magic, Spell Diligence.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of advanced mage talents can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/black-mage/mage-talents/#advanced-mage-talents\">Advanced Mage Talents</a></li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Black Mage Talent"],["Black Mage Talent, Advanced"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"mageTalentsMagus","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"5FHA3GajKQ7zXT4q"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ED5bDQ3ftaU77qdI","name":"Bypass Spell Resistance","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 17th level, the black mage&rsquo;s command of magic is such that he may unravel a creature&rsquo;s natural resistance to magic. A black mage may reduce a target&rsquo;s spell resistance by his black mage level, once per day per target. In addition, a black mage ignores energy resistance equal to half his caster level.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"bypassSpellResistance","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"tQz6eArt3HCp85FI"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"FygL6Z5GFe05kGBZ","name":"Metamagic Enhancement","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A black mage is a master at manipulating magical forces. At 5th level, as a move action, he reduces the cost of any metamagic feat known by one MP less than standard. For example, a 5th level black mage casts a spell with the Empower feat for 1 extra MP cost higher than the original spell. The metamagic enhancement can only be applied to one enhancement per spell. This ability does not affect the Heighten Spell feat. At 11th level and 17th level, the adjusted MP cost is reduced one additional MP. The adjusted enhancement can never reduce the base spell below its original level. A black mage may use this ability up to 3 times per day.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"move"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":3,"max":3,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"metamagicEnhancement","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""