{"_id":"HIB4O1Wiecj5G9aA","name":"Damage Control","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, when the magus invokes Elemental Shield to defend against a radius spell he has casted, he doubles its efficiency. At 10th level, the magus&rsquo;s elemental shield triples the amount, and at 17th level, it quadruples.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This ability replaces dark affliction.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Defencive"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"damageControl","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"H5DrUUt6rWHpGZUW"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"JNJSPFR10AidWuMV","name":"Living Catastrophe","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 20th level, the magus becomes a mortal instrument of mayhem and destruction, and as long as he exists, the world will never be safe. The magus increases the effect of the Widen Spell metamagic feat by an additional +200% (base radius x5).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This ability replaces black wizard.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"],["Metamagic"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"livingCatastrophe","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"o5VqWUcZmEp2p4PW"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"JulEk4lz0VijX5XO","name":"Shaped Area","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 19th level, a black mage can alter areas of effect for spells that use one of the following shapes: burst, cone, cylinder, emanation, or spread. The alteration consists of creating spaces within the spell&rsquo;s area or effect that are not subject to the spell. The minimum dimension for these spaces is a 5 ft. cube. Furthermore, any shapeable spells have a minimum dimension of 5 ft. instead of 10 ft. He can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + his Intelligence modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"shapedArea","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffse