{"_id":"KGf86ttQ2jNIFl9M","name":"Sudden Metamagic","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 15th level, the black mage may apply any single metamagic feat that he knows to a 6th-level spell or lower that he is about to cast. This does not alter the level of the spell or the MP cost. The black mage can apply a metamagic feat in this way a number of times per day equal to his Intelligence modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"],["Metamagic"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"suddenMetamagic","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"xocTwMgyniT0TV9H"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"LQv5pXGrm1nPHXTJ","name":"Limit Break: Ultima Weapons","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This Limit Break allows the black mage to infuse all his allies and himself with magic to increase their destructive might. For himself, and allies in a 30-ft radius, for a duration of 1 round + 1 round per four black mage levels after 1st, all wielded natural, unarmed, and manufactured weapons are treated as magical and deal an additional 1d4 non-elemental damage + 1d4 per four black mage levels after 1st. This limit break requires only a swift action.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Limit Break"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":2,"type":"action"}},"duration":{"value":"1+floor(([@classes.blackMage.level]-1) / 4)","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"personal","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"none"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"charges","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"@attributes.limitbreak.value"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"circle","size":"30","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"0","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"Fast Healing [[(2+(floor(([@classes.whiteMageBase.level]-1) / 4)*2)]] with a duration of [[(1+(floor(([@classes.whiteMageBase.level]-1) / 4)))]]","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"limitBreakUltimaWeapons","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":true,"nonlethal":true,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":""},"flags":{},"effects":[]}
{"_id":"LlrkcfKvNsehx2IC","name":"Art of Destruction","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st, 5th, 9th, 13th, and 17th level,&nbsp;the magus increases the destructive scale for a number of his spells. He selects one of the following area-types each time he gains this class ability. Any time he casts a damaging area-effect spell, he gains the listed benefit. He may take the same area-type multiple times, its effects stack.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Burst:&nbsp;</em>Increase radius by 5 feet.</li>\n<li><em>Cone:&nbsp;</em>Increase cone-radius by 10 feet.</li>\n<li><em>Cylinder:&nbsp;</em>Increase radius by 5 ft and Height by 10 ft.</li>\n<li><em>Line:&nbsp;</em>Increase the lines length by 20 feet or its Width by 5 ft.</li>\n<li><em>Wall:&nbsp;</em>Increase length by 10 ft and Height by 5 ft.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This ability replaces black magery.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"artOfDestruction","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"ADVnXvZV2nCJx8aV"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"N3ZEkTlUSO0L3AUb","name":"Black Magery","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level and every four black mage levels thereafter, a black mage increases his power with his spells of 1st level or higher. This ability applies only to spells that he casts as a&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">black</span> mage, not to those he might have by virtue of levels in another class. At each such opportunity, he can choose from the list of the following (with a maximum of 2 per):</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Elemental Mastery:</em>&nbsp;This increases the black mage&rsquo;s caster level by 1 for all spells with an elemental descriptor.</li>\n<li><em>Increased Damage:</em> This increases any damage spell from the black mage spell list the black mage casts by 1 extra die of the appropriate type. This allows you to overcome any damage cap a spell might restrict you to. Only applies once per casting, such spells with multiple attacks (such as Ruin) only applies to 1 missile.</li>\n<li><em>Spell Mastery:</em>&nbsp;This increases the DC for all of the black mage&rsquo;s spells by 1.</li>\n<li><em>Spell Penetration:</em> This increases the black mage&rsquo;s caster level checks by 1 made to overcome a creature&rsquo;s spell resistance. This stacks with the Spell Penetration feat.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"blackMagery","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"7PVBxBxR507ICyRg"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"O6MeHLT832yYygy3","name":"Focused Caster","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Beginning at 3rd level, a black mage may roll twice on any concentration check and take the higher result.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"focusedCaster","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"qsxnZ6uR6A1GwppA"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"UENaE6Y9JV8xIqzb","name":"Mage Talents","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a black mage gains experience, he learns a number of talents that assist him in manipulating spells and other forms of magic. At 2nd level and every two levels thereafter, a black mage gains one mage talent. A black mage cannot select an individual talent more than once. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a black mage&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of mage talents can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/black-mage/mage-talents/\">Mage Talents</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"advanced-mage-talents\">Advanced Mage Talents</h3>\n<p>At 12th, and every two levels thereafter, a black mage learns further talents to assist him in manipulating spells and other forms of magic. He may choose one of the following advanced mage talents in place of a mage talent. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a black mage&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of advanced mage talents can be found here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/core-classes/black-mage/mage-talents/#advanced-mage-talents\">Advanced Mage Talents</a></li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Black Mage Talent"],["Black Mage Talent, Advanced"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"mageTalents","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"5FHA3GajKQ7zXT4q"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"YH4wpAedyjdPAuUs","name":"Loremaster","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 11th level, the black mage becomes a master of lore and can take 10 on any Knowledge skill check that he has ranks in. A black mage can choose not to take 10 and can instead roll normally. In addition, once per day, the black mage can take 20 on any Knowledge skill check as a standard action.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Skills"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"loremaster","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":true,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"Ekd8uL2454ABaFVZ"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"aKEHuiU9muGFbj7N","name":"Mass Destruction","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 5th level, the magus gains the <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/feats/metamagic-feats/widen-spell/\">Widen Spell</a> feat. If he already possesses this feat then he chooses another metamagic or item creation feat instead. At 10th level, the MP cost of the Widen Spell metamagic feat is reduced by 1 for any area-effect spell he casts. At 15th level, increase the effects of the Widen Spell metamagic feat by +100% (base radius x3). At 20th level, the Widen Spell metamagic feat costs no additional MP for any black mage area-effect spell he casts.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This ability replaces metamagic enhancement.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Feat"],["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"massDestruction","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":