{"_id":"bMp3Q22kh5h2T5kQ","name":"Spell Proficiency","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Black mages are considered to have the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/precise-shot-combat/\">Precise Shot</a>&nbsp;feat while casting spells, using class features that require ranged touch or using any magical items that require ranged touch.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Feat"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"spellProficiency","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"Wwin3imVyo2VwzLe"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ggRpa0Xvn8Pke3n7","name":"Clear Mind","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 5th level, a black mage can regain his MP quicker. The black mage must be relaxed and must be free from overt distractions, such as combat raging nearby or other loud noises. For example, he could be riding in the back of a carriage and benefit from this ability. The black mage does not gain this recovery if he is asleep or unconscious. The black mage regains 1 MP per hour. This increases by 1 for every five black mage levels after 5th</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Recovery"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"clearMind","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"6qlRzaGEStCNE4qs"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"i6KehADsb0ynnfbO","name":"1 MP Spell","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 18th level, three times per day, as a free action, a black mage can reduce the cost of his next spell to 1 MP. The use of this ability cannot be used with metamagic feats.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"1MpSpell","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"qd4a7FqOQwA8pGBc"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"jQ3rdwIWykkLpjR8","name":"Dark Affliction","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, when the black mage casts any black magic enfeebling spells, the target of said spell takes a penalty to saving throws against any further of the same status effect equal to the spell level of the spell for any similar subsequent effects or spells for 1 round, even from effects or spells made by allies. This effect does not stack with itself.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"darkAffliction","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"eGA9bQkEiq0526Mt"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"jwbuV6eiLJ6YiWaz","name":"Spells/Cantrips - Black Mage","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>A black mage casts black magic spells which are drawn the <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells-by-class/black-mage/\">black mage spell list</a>. A black mage begins play with 3 1st level black mage spells of his choice. The black mage also selects a number of additional 1st-level spells equal to his&nbsp;Intelligence&nbsp;modifier to add to his list of spells. Each time a character attains a new black mage level, he gains two spells of his choice to add to his list of spells. The two free spells must be of spell levels he can cast. Like most mages, a black mage can find or purchase scrolls with spells to add to his repertoire.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To learn or cast a spell, the black mage must have an Intelligence score equal to at least 10 + the spell level (Int 11 for 1st-<wbr />level spells, Int 12 for 2nd-<wbr />level spells, and so forth). The Difficulty Class for a saving throw against a black mage&rsquo;s spell is 10 + the spell level + the black mage&rsquo;s Intelligence modifier. In addition, a black mage gains additional MP for having a high attribute (Intelligence&mdash;see&nbsp;<strong>Table: Bonus MP per Day (by Spell Level)</strong> on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/mp-system/\">MP System page</a>).</p>\n<p>Black mages learn a number of cantrips, or 0-<wbr />level spells. These spells are cast like any other spell, but they do not consume MP and may be used again. Black mages begin with 4 0-<wbr />level spells and gain an additional 0-<wbr />level spell every three levels after 1st level.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Cantrips"],["Spells"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"spellscantripsBlackMage","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Black Mage"],["Magus"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","attack":{"parts":[]}},"flags":{"importid":"tx4003rMl48Tbwkh"},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"ltfTacrkLm1MTlT1","name":"Selective Targets","permission":{"default":0,"e1nAgjLmIKiSwmCp":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 13th level, the black mage may select up to one target per point of Intelligence bonus to exclude from any area-<wbr />of-<wbr />effect spell cast, or double the number of targets affected by a spell. In the first application, the targets are engulfed in the effect, but do not suffer any of the effects. This is a target-<wbr />based exclusion; other opponents sharing the excluded target&rsquo;s space are still affected by the spell. In the second case, when a spell description specifies an effect of &ldquo;one creature per level,&rdquo; the black mage may instead affect up to two creatures per level.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Casting"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"","long":null},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noStr":false,"noDex":false,"oneInt":false,"oneWis":false,"oneCha":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"selectiveTargets","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"featType":"classFea